MAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA5|title=Popular Lectures on Astronomy: Delivered at the Royal Observatory of Paris|last=Arago|first=Fran\u00e7ois|last2=Lardner|first2=Dionysius|date=1845|publisher=Greeley & McElrath|language=en}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=leon2006>''Mems/Nems: Volume 1 Handbook Techniques and Applications Design Methods'' By Cornelius T. Leondes -- Springer 2006 Page 203</ref>\n\n<ref name=lewis2008>''X-Ray Lasers 2008: Proceedings of the 11th International Conference'' By Ciaran Lewis, Dave Riley == Springer 2009 Page 34</ref>\n\n<ref name=lieb185>{{cite journal| doi = 10.1002/jlac.18560980112 | title = Ueber Versilberung und Vergoldung von Glas | journal = Annalen der Chemie und Pharmacie | volume = 98 | issue = 1 | year = 1856 | pages = 132\u2013139 | first = Justus | last = Liebig}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=love>{{cite web|url=http://www.hplovecraft.com/writings/texts/fiction/trap.aspx|title=\"The Trap\" by H. P. Lovecraft|work=hplovecraft.com}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=mark1996>{{cite journal | last1 = Smith | first1 = A. Mark | year = 1996 | title = Ptolemy's Theory of Visual Perception: An English Translation of the \"Optics\" with Introduction and Commentary | url = | journal = Transactions of the American Philosophical Society |series=New Series | volume = 86 | issue = 2| pages = iii\u2013300 | doi=10.2307/3231951| jstor = 3231951 }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=mart1995>{{cite book |title=Self-awareness in Animals and Humans: Developmental Perspectives |author1=Marten, K. |author2=Psarakos, S. |lastauthoramp=yes |chapter=Evidence of self-awareness in the bottlenose dolphin (''Tursiops truncatus'') |editor=Parker, S.T. |editor2=Mitchell, R. |editor3=Boccia, M. |pages=361\u2013379 |year=1995 |publisher=Cambridge University Press |chapter-url=http://earthtrust.org/delbook.html |accessdate=2008-10-04 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081013081149/http://earthtrust.org/delbook.html |archivedate=13 October 2008 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n\n<ref name=matt2004>''The Founda